sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant DesktopApp as Desktop Application
    participant System as System

    User->>DesktopApp: Launch Application
    DesktopApp->>System: Request Initialization
    System-->>DesktopApp: Send Initialization Data
    DesktopApp-->>User: Display Interface
    User->>DesktopApp: Interact with Features
    DesktopApp->>System: Send User Actions
    System-->>DesktopApp: Process Actions
    DesktopApp-->>User: Update Interface